<div class="KonaBody"><p>An introduction to Docker networking and its components.</p>
<p>In this guide, you’ll learn about the essential components of Docker networking, which have evolved from coupling simple Docker abstractions and powerful network components such as Linux bridges and Open vSwitch. We’ll also discuss the next generation of Docker networking, which is called libnetwork.<br />
<span id="more-4542"></span></p>
